The Progressives Governors Forum (PGF) has felicitated with President Muhammadu Buhari who marked his 77th birthday yesterday. The PGF Chairman and Governor of Kebbi State, Atiku Bagudu, in a statement he personally signed, said the forum was proud to associate with President Buhari who he described as a ‘role model and an example of incorrigible leadership to this generation.’ Bagudu thanked President Buhari for his selfless service to Nigeria. “The Progressive Governors Forum wishes His Excellency, President Buhari, GCFR, a happy birthday and also say a big thank you for your selfless service to our dear country. “We are very proud of you and your brave and fearless leadership. You have been a role model and an example of incorrigible leadership to this generation. We proudly hold you as someone worthy of emulation.” Judge APC when our mandate expires — Okorocha NASS leadership: APC governors back Lawan, Gbajabiamila Oshiomhole’s shaky hold on APC